snippet.title: Best VGM 2374 - Double Dragon II : The Revenge (Arcade) - Lumber Stockhouse (Mission 2)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Arcade
Double Dragon II : The Revenge (1988)
Lumber Stockhouse (Mission 2)
Kazunaka Yamane
